description: Beautifully renovated two bedroom two full bath front facing penthouse loft conveniently located in the Seaport! With over 1,700 square feet of living space enjoy a sun-filled open living area with separate dining area off the gourmet kitchen with a raised living room. This flexible space is spacious also accommodates an office area. The primary bedroom is luxurious with plenty of room for a sitting area. There are multiple custom closets. The en-suite bath is sumptuous with a separated double sink area, a large shower and a stand-alone soaking tub. The second bedroom is lovely with a large closet and plenty of room for a small sitting area and a gorgeous frosted barn door for privacy. Featuring hardwood floors throughout, numerous windows for optimal lighting, C/A, and direct access garage parking space.  The building has gorgeous common areas, elevator, and a roof deck. This penthouse also has the roof rights to a large area for you to custom build the private deck of your dreams.
